                      <span>2002-06-21</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>This is the BEST book I've read in the last 20 years!!  A must read for anyone interested in the Utopian vision of radical movements. I learned a great deal about the reparations movement, Black feminism, and a movement no one is talking about-Surrealism. And it's beautifully written.</span>
                  
              
